<br />
http://www.esquire.com/blogs/food-for-men/four-hour-gravlax-recipe-14985897<br />
<br />
<br />
As for fish-borne parasites they are only a major concern for freshwater fish because those parasites are those that can cause zoonotic infections, such as tapeworm. Otherwise with saltwater fish it is as Michael Chu stated.</div>
					<hr size="1" noshade />
				
